event.title: 1:20 a.m. Saturday, GPD spokesman Keith Kameg said

data.event: Gainesville Police Officer Shawn Barnes saw three men acting suspiciously in a parking lot near the 1000 block of Southeast Fourth Avenue at 1:20 a.m. Saturday, GPD spokesman Keith Kameg said.
According to the GPD arrest report, records indicated that the car was reported stolen on Wednesday.
